      <method name="UB_set" c:identifier="hkl_sample_UB_set" throws="1">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="hkl/hkl-sample.c"
             line="620">Set the UB matrix using an external UB matrix. In fact you give
the UB matrix but only the U matrix of the sample is affected by
this operation. We keep the B matrix constant.
U * B = UB -&gt; U = UB * B^-1
